query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total,
  SUM(CASE WHEN isServiceable = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as active,
  SUM(CASE WHEN isServiceable = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as excluded,
  SUM(CASE WHEN isServiceable IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as null_status
FROM supplierRates 
WHERE supplierId = 210001
